00:30:28.440 --> 00:30:31.420
Players will earn currency
called dimensional shards

00:30:31.420 --> 00:30:34.200
by participating in different
events over the next five week

00:30:34.200 --> 00:30:35.610
period.

00:30:35.610 --> 00:30:39.930
The more they participate,
the more shards they'll earn.

00:30:39.930 --> 00:30:41.880
Using this currency,
they can open up

00:30:41.880 --> 00:30:46.420
new dimensional rifts, which are
limited time quests with very

00:30:46.420 --> 00:30:48.120
valuable rewards.

00:30:48.120 --> 00:30:50.400
They can choose when they
want to open these rifts,

00:30:50.400 --> 00:30:54.400
so they aren't locked to
any start or end time.

00:30:54.400 --> 00:30:59.070
And this new event is the
result of the hard work

00:30:59.070 --> 00:31:03.210
of countless talented
people all working together

00:31:03.210 --> 00:31:07.020
so that the LiveOps team
just has to hit a button

00:31:07.020 --> 00:31:08.061
